You’ve heard the name for a year… but do you know what Machki really means?
It’s not just a brand. It’s a feeling. A memory. A name that’s been mine since forever. 🩷

Sharing the heart behind Machki — the name my dad gave me, and the dream I turned into reality 😇

#meaningbehindthename #machki #fatherdaughter #womeninspiringwomen #dadanddaughter #jewelrywithmeaning #smallbusinessindia #madewithlove❤️

Grwm to celebrate @machki.in ‘s 1 year Celebration 🎉💃🏼💖 also revealing the most asked question today at 5pm! 

.
#grwmreel #celebrationoflove #machki #accessories #dressup #grwmoutfit #softgirlaesthetic #withlove

Behind every pretty package you receive, there’s chaos, trial & error, and a lot of back-and-forth between me and my brother 😂

Shipping was one of the toughest things to figure out — from delays to damaged parcels to learning what works best for YOU.
We didn’t have all the answers, but we always had each other (and Google 😅).

This is Part 4 of our journey — real, raw, and still figuring it out.
If you’re building something from scratch, just know — you’re not alone. 💌

.
#startupjourney #struggles #behindthescenes #siblingteam #founders #entrepreneurlife #reality #customerlove #shiprocket #machkiaccessories

Some bonds are built by blood, some by business — and we got both 🫶
For the first time, meet the other half of this dream — my brother, my biggest support, and the reason so much of Machki works behind the scenes 💪🏻

💻 From building the website to handling packaging runs, we’ve been figuring it all out together since day one 🌻

This journey hasn’t just been about jewelry, it’s been about people — and he’s been mine 💖
Here’s to the chaos, the late nights, and the best kind of teamwork.
